    Ominous slamed the screen to the floor in defeat. She was now fully aware 
and it would be more the difficult to break her.
    "Im Ominous Prime. Commander of the Energonian Empire." He sighed, "And i 
have converted you to one of us. Look." He pointed to an image reflector 
across the room. Her silver body looked back at them.
    "Impressive, yes?" He smiled.
